# .omc: explicitly ignore ephemeral dirs, persistent artifacts tracked by default
# Using **/.omc/<dir> patterns covers both root and nested .omc/ dirs.
# Trade-off: must update this list if new ephemeral dirs are added to .omc/
**/.omc/state/
**/.omc/sessions/
**/.omc/autopilot/
**/.omc/drafts/
**/.omc/handoffs/
**/.omc/logs/
**/.omc/research/
**/.omc/prd*.json
**/.omc/progress.txt
.worktrees/
.claude/backups/

.agent_key
